@node "Main" "ASC_SEND_english.guide"

                     Welcome to @{b}ASCII_SEND@{ub}

      In this Distribution (3.3 of 6-10-95) 4 different Programs can be found:
  
      1. Mui_ASCSEND,  The whole thing...featuring a nice MUI-GUI,
                       Arexx-Port and a lot of other goodies
                       needs @{"MUI" link "mui" 0}
                       Version: 1.19
       2. ASCSEND    , Simple version, no GUI, no Arexx,
                       doesn't need  MUI
                       This is only the Ascii-SENDER
                       Version 1.14
       3. IREC       , InputEvent-Recorder part of
                       MUI_ASCSEND,
                       doesn't need MUI
                       Version 1.4
       4.CLI_ASCSEND , command-line only version;
                       Version 1.1


                     @{"  Disclaimer           " link "Disclaimer" 0}
                     @{"  Overview             " link "Overview" 0}
